 dusty volume against another and carried them to his nook behind the stand. Additional eccentricities were noted: his light remained on practically until dawn; he was oddly unsociable.

We hear Anton’s voice: “That fine gentleman shows off. We should give him a closer look.”

“I’ll sell him the pipe,” said Gustav.

